        We develop new web applications in a fast and secure manner
      </p>
    </article>
    <ul class="what-list">
      <li class="what-list-item">
        <div class="what-illustration">
          <img class="h-36" src="/assets/vector/semantic-web.svg" alt="linked data">
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h4 class="what-title">Powerful single-page web applications
          </h4>
          <p class="what-text">Experience speed and power with ember JS
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="what-list-item">
        <div class="what-illustration">
          <img class="h-36" src="/assets/vector/linked-data.svg" alt="linked data">
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h4 class="what-title">Semantic Knowledge Graphs
          </h4>
          <p class="what-text">Uncover the links between your data
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="what-list-item">
        <div class="what-illustration">
          <img class="h-36" src="/assets/vector/open-data.svg" alt="linked data">
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h4 class="what-title">Microservices</h4>
          <p class="what-text">A chameleonic back-end service environment with semantic.works</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="what-list-item">
        <div class="what-illustration">
          <img class="h-36" src="/assets/vector/open-standards.svg" alt="linked data">
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h4 class="what-title">Linked Open Data </h4>
          <p class="what-text">Empower data with semantics and open data standards
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

